dct_description_sm: 2 inset maps at larger scale showing coasts near Pemba and Zanzibar islands and The Shire Highlands south of Lake Nyassa.
Shows territories by color, waterways, land routes, regional names, territory "leased to King Leopold."
Dated from presence of "protectorate" west and south of Lake Nyassa (Malawi).
